all require downtrend (say at least 2/3)

hammer _> (open-low) >= (close-open) , (high - close) -> negligible value (2-5%)

inverse hammer _> (high - close) >= (close - open) , (open-low) -> negligible value (2-5%)

bullish engulf _> bearish -> bullish, open2 < close1, close2 > open1

piercing line _> bearish -> bullish, open2 < close1, close2 = open1 * 0.5-0.66

3 soliders -> bullish -> bearish -> bearish -> bearish
